"замість того, щоб друкувати його:"

#: ../../tutorial/controlflow.rst:537
msgid ""
">>> def fib2(n):  # return Fibonacci series up to n\n"
"...     \"\"\"Return a list containing the Fibonacci series up to n.\"\"\"\n"
"...     result = []\n"
"...     a, b = 0, 1\n"
